'''Aber''' was the primary [[Star/Legends|star]] of the [[Abron system]]. The star was a [[Red dwarf/Legends|red dwarf]] and primarily emitted energy in the [[Infrared/Legends|infrared]] spectrum. It was orbited by the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Alpheridies/Legends|Alpheridies]], home planet of the [[Near-Human]] [[Miraluka/Legends|Miraluka]]. Because of the infrared light, the Miraluka were unable to see naturally. They could, however, "see" their surroundings through [[The Force/Legends|the Force]].

